  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective observational cohort study of women with gestational diabetes (GDM) based on the
      'International Association of Pregnancy Study Groups' (IADPSG) criteria. The overall aim is
      to evaluate the knowledge regarding GDM of women with GDM and to evaluate the satisfaction of
      women with GDM about the education they receive (given in group or individually). Normal
      routine care is followed and evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
